Original_Description:
Introducing the Millet Rava Combo! The perfect blend made from unpolished millets, clean of dirt, sand and stones. Gluten free and easy to cook, this 4 pack can be used to make many delicious recipes like Phirni, Kitchadi, Laddu and Kesari. Vacuum-packed to retain freshness without any preservatives or additives, and part of the 2023 International Year of Millets - this 8lb pack is the perfect way to buy more and save more.
Package contains 2lb Kodo Millet Rava (Coarse), 2lb Foxtail Millet Rava (
Coarse
), 2lb Barnyard Millet Rava (
Coarse
) & 2lb Little Millet Rava (
Coarse
). Total 4 packs & 8lb.

